<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l4"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> beſant vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . daʒ er der <expan>lorencʒın<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l5">gwalt das gwelb aufgeſagt hab / ʒu den <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> do ſıe dennoch wıtıb vnd eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l6">hauſfraw niht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . als er eẅch das vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nehſt <expan>eygentlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l7">VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> . ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / hett Jr oder eẅr hauſfraw dar = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l8"><expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . ıht ʒu <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> . ſo <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch oder <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> ſchein = </ab>
