<ab facs="#facs_140_r2l16">vor Jm <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſein </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_140" id="70r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Jacob<ex>en</ex></expan> Fuchsmag, lantvogt zu
                                <expan>Höhstett<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft"><expan cert="medium">no<ex>ta</ex></expan>
</note>
</app><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Fuchsmag, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Karl Colers etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                        <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> besant und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Der hat uns
                        <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>, daz er der
                            <expan>Lorenczin<ex>n</ex></expan> Gwalt das gwelb aufgesagt hab zu den
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>, do sie dennoch witib und ewr
                        hausfraw niht <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, als er ewch das und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> nehst
                            <expan>eygentlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hab. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b
                        </expan>so <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, hett ir oder ewr hausfraw
                                dar<expan>üb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> iht zu <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>, so
                                <expan>wölt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch oder
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> schein<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> und <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        hausfrawn <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>m</expan> gwalt
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von im <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des
                        reichs <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und mainen und getrawn ewch auch noch
                        wol, ir lat ewch des <expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan>; möcht oder wölt ir
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> daran niht ein
                            <expan>genüg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so spricht der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> Karl Coler, er well
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> mit ewch <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        für den edeln <expan>wolgeborne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ludweig<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Öting<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> von Payern vicztum, und ewch eins
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> vor im
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> sein. </ab></div>
</div></body>
